      <details class="faq__item" open>
        <summary class="faq__q">
          <span class="faq__q-text">When will I see results?</span>
          <span class="faq__icon">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="faq__a">Hydration and calming products feel different on day one. Brightening and anti-aging actives need 2–4 weeks of consistent use, with the full benefit compounding over 6–8 weeks.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq__item">
        <summary class="faq__q">
          <span class="faq__q-text">Can I layer this with my other actives?</span>
          <span class="faq__icon">+</span>
        </summary>
