          <span class="faq__q-text">Will it cause a reaction?</span>
          <span class="faq__icon">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="faq__a">Our formulas use clinically tested ingredients at safe concentrations. Mild tingling can happen when introducing new actives — patch-test on your jawline for a few days first if you're highly reactive.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq__item">
